{
  "texts": [
    "As a deep neural network architecture, the authors use both LSTM and BiLSTM layers.",
    "They also combine Bi-LSTM and CRF.More recently, Jin et al. [85][86][87] focused on approaches transforming entities in a knowledge base (KB) to an entity graph to apply graph-based algorithms to it.",
    "The idea of their first work [86] is to construct an entity graph by using links between entities.",
    "They also used both graph structure and entity features for fine-grained NER.",
    "They applied an attributed and predictive network embedding model to construct entity features and structure the graph."
  ]
}